        "Recovery"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，Recovery是一个复合状态。那两条路径分别对应什么？我猜测一条是ClassroomService的恢复，另一条是ContentCDN的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Recovery",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的。ClassroomService那条路径是从Replica提升为Tail节点，涉及PromotingFromReplica、RunningAsTail、Transferring、Demoting，最后回到RunningAsReplica。CDN那条是从Waiting开始，经过Ingesting、PromotingFromCandidate到达RunningAsTail。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PromotingFromReplica",
        "RunningAsTail",
        "Transferring",
        "Demoting",
        "RunningAsReplica",
        "Waiting",
        "Ingesting",
