      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经画出了Recovery复合状态内部的两条路径。另外我在外层加了两个状态：RunningAsTail和RunningAsReplica，分别包含LMS门户与ClassroomService、StudentDB的关联。这样正常状态和恢复状态就区分开了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "RunningAsTail",
        "RunningAsReplica",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，RunningAsTail里面的连接有点问题。LMS门户应该只连ClassroomService，但StudentDB应该在RunningAsReplica里。还有，Recovery入口应该从LMS门户直接进来，不是从其他状态跳转。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Recovery",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "RunningAsTail",
