    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "看起来对了。再确认一下CDN那条路径的终点：PromotingFromCandidate之后也是RunningAsTail，这意味着CDN恢复完成后和ClassroomService一样都进入Tail节点状态，对吧？",
